<item>
            <title>[LU-3610] The argument names of mgs_write_log_pool() is misplaced</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3610</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The argument &apos;fsname&apos; and &apos;poolname&apos; of mgs_write_log_pool() is misplaced. &apos;fsname&apos; should be replaced by &apos;poolname&apos;, and &apos;poolname&apos; should be replaced by &apos;fsname&apos;. That is not a problem for machine, but might confuse some code readers, e.g. me.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
